<subSubSection pageId="26" pageNumber="300" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="26.[160,1155,1327,1386]" pageId="26" pageNumber="300">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[160,426,1327,1351]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="300">Differential diagnosis.</emphasis>
Antennomere III as long as pedicel; median labral tooth as developed as lateral teeth. Epipleura wide. Pronotum yellow, elytron black.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="26" pageNumber="300" type="discussion">
